{"tid":2227424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"友愛邨公園10少年煲蠟　引發爆炸火球竄半空","createTime":"2020-10-02T18:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T19:44:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b39a823f4d663cf87d08a4d6e21600cea44942c8","tid":2227424,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"今日(3日)凌晨零時許，屯門友愛邨平台公園突傳出爆炸響聲，並有一團火球竄向半空，住客見狀大驚報警。消防接報到場，攜手提滅火筒將火勢救熄，事件中無人受傷，亦無波及場內設施，惟地面遺下大片紅色蠟漬，不排除有人煲蠟引起火警。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，事發時有街坊目睹約有10名年約15至16歲少年聚集，未幾即見火光熊熊。警方及後翻查現場一帶閉路電視錄影片段，追查涉案少年。"},{"pid":"6db2a94eea13c6fb8d11b5146bc578f7966ea5b1","tid":2227424,"uid":155815,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"呢代仲有人玩架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年我果區完全係0喎"},{"pid":"6a119fd49eea700fde29599fcd9ec87af1a803f1","tid":2227424,"uid":30900,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"文化傳承 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d60087bab16765d8641582776e882cec63eacb1","tid":2227424,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:38.000Z","msg":"燒到狗屋就最好"},{"pid":"850d85ef12670a3dc7681c5b68ffac3decfc78e0","tid":2227424,"uid":17008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:49.000Z","msg":"香港仲有人煲蠟 admire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df181bd13e690dafae98503d901f32acfafe11bd","tid":2227424,"uid":189417,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a119fd49eea700fde29599fcd9ec87af1a803f1","tid":2227424,"uid":30900,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"文化傳承 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p1.pstatp.com/large/113f30008dd2835a0fe70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum